```{r bileducts 33079423, include=FALSE}

PMID_33079423 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('33079423', database = 'PubMed')

citation_33079423 <- paste0(PMID_33079423$journal,' ', PMID_33079423$year, ' ', PMID_33079423$month,';', PMID_33079423$volume,'(', PMID_33079423$number,'):', PMID_33079423$pages)

PubMed_33079423 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_33079423$eprint)

doi_33079423 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_33079423$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
